Package: Refinitiv
Type: Package
Title: Connect to LSEG/Refinitiv Eikon and DataStream from R
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Laurens van der Burg
Maintainer: Laurens van der Burg <laurens@ggbo.eu>
Description: Zero-config R interface to LSEG Workspace (formerly Refinitiv Eikon)
    and DataStream. Auto-detects the running terminal, connects via direct JSON
    API calls, and provides opt-in session-scoped request caching. Includes
    historical and snapshot data retrieval, real-time WebSocket streaming, ESG,
    consensus estimates, ownership data, custom instruments, and news. DataStream
    access is provided via the 'DatastreamDSWS2R' package. This package is in no
    way affiliated with LSEG, Refinitiv, Eikon or Datastream. Use at own risk.
License: LGPL (>= 2.0, < 3) | Mozilla Public License
